{"tid":1819470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾香港人（抵你班垃圾黃絲輸）","createTime":"2020-01-10T22:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T00:16:26.000Z","uid":342968,"like":36,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a02cff8edf5cffab6e10de15ee36fe9e83e6c5f1","tid":1819470,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T22:16:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭化閪<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得6月頭 和理非同勇武係政總對抗極權？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jAYo3Hf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjAYo3Hf.jpg&h=f9bb9a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xGueOW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xGueOW.jpg&h=2118e700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果陣 我自己都好驚 好驚會失敗<br />\n<br />\n但有各位手足陪伴 我先有勇氣繼續<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得7月1號 攻入立法會既決心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w9zr1u3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9zr1u3.jpg&h=0484f33f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzquZgK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzquZgK.jpg&h=39ebfd81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOfrg3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOfrg3q.jpg&h=b1754eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果陣真係好撚淆 但手足都係互信大家 邊有捉鬼呢樣野？<br />\n<br />\n鬼一齊都有 佢冇樣睇 無跡可尋 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">因為佢住左係你心入面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfFbtbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfFbtbo.jpg&h=da525ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你地記唔記得呢班人啊 就係佢地無差別攻擊<br />\n<br />\n官警黑鐵 呢個仇仲未報架！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p82X8cu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp82X8cu.jpg&h=22be4d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxshoLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxshoLQ.jpg&h=37484915&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DsNk5Za.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDsNk5Za.jpg&h=d5d58b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幕真係睇到香港人好嬲好嬲<br />\n冇人可以原諒佢地 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YfFuZn0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYfFuZn0.jpg&h=9d8476ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dusEB9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdusEB9G.jpg&h=a85af734&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Gv61Bq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Gv61Bq.jpg&h=475c3b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記唔記得經過呢日檢討之後 大家變成真正be water <br />\n快閃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後唔撚再打喇<br />\n<br />\n反正之後大家都掛住捉鬼 政治潔癖 分化 割蓆<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講一樣好簡單既野<br />\n<br />\n諗返大家運動之前 <br />\n齊心協力 齊上齊落<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不督灰<br />\n我地先行到呢一步<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足 攰就抖下啦 多謝你地守護我地<br />\n文宣文絲 你地都付出好多 涯住<br />\n冇野做既和理非 麻煩你地出去遊行 叫大聲啲好冇<br />\n<br />\n最後一句 唔好嫌我沉氣<br />\n唔好再公審自己人<br />\n因為 因為 因為<br />\n大家都好愛好愛好愛香港<br />\n<br />\n儘管佢做既野太左膠<br />\n但希望大家手下留情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#愛比捉鬼強<br />\n<br />\n見到勇武巴 不仿攬下佢 拍下佢膊頭<br />\n見到和理非 不如講聲加油<br />\n<br />\n咁樣先係手足<br />\n<br />\n期待再見呢一幕"},{"pid":"cb343437a9488b777f3667fe9ec628b705fd20ab","tid":1819470,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T22:17:48.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到 求下你幫手十推"},{"pid":"6a5c4a5c9be95aa44fab04afe77f25dfc41240f2","tid":1819470,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T22:18:03.000Z","msg":"推空氣"},{"pid":"e85e4f47391a81708ff5ce25d9de44675b9f4437","t